    public static final String CONST_GAL_TEAM_ITEM_DES2 ="After earning his bachelors in Computer Science from University of California, Berkeley, Harry Founded his first company in January 2015. He later became the Head of Data Products at the Club Factory. In 2018, he Co-Founded two companies, Lino Network, where he served as CTO, and DLive. In April 2021, he Co-Founded Galxe, where he joined as Project Lead.";
    public static final String CONST_GAL_TEAM_ITEM_DES3 ="Xinlu has a strong background in engineering, beginning as a Software Engineer at MicroStrategy in 2011, later becoming a Technical Leader. From here, they became an Engineering Manager at the Club Factory, then Head of Engineering at the Lino Network, and finally they Co-Founded Galxe as Tech Lead.";
    public static final String CONST_GAL_TEAM_ITEM_DES4 ="Anne began her management career as the Business Development Manager for Préambule Communication. Three years later, she joined the advertising agency BRAD as their Coordinator. In 2017, she became VIBRANT Marketing’s Strategist and four years later became the Cultural Strategist for the French Shop. In March 2022, she joined Galxe as their Marketing Manager before becoming their Chief Marketing Officer later that same year.";
    public static final String CONST_GAL_TEAM_ITEM_DES5 ="Brian has a strong business background, in 2016 he Co-Founded LOUD a creative design studio followed by Button Shortcuts two years later. In 2020, he Founded Wefunder, serving as its Founder-In-Residence, Growth and Business Development. In 2021, he became Republic’s Digital Community Operations Manager before joining Galxe as their ecosystem Development Manager in 2022.";
